---
middleBoxTitle: Contribute
---
middleBox: This resource is far from being complete, if you want to know where the development is headed, check the [Road Map](/road-map). If you spot any mistake, or you think something could be explained better, open an issue at the [project repository](https://github.com/roberto-arista/PythonForDesigners). I also accept to review *pull requests*.
---
